OL,3,CMan jailed for threatening to kill MP
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FA man jailed for making repeated death
OL,7,Fthreats against his MP has died in
OL,8,Fprison.
OL,10,FBenjamin Clarke, 32, was sentenced to
OL,11,F18 months in jail in May after making
OL,12,Frepeated death threats to his MP Sam
OL,13,FRushworth.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Prisons and
OL,16,FProbation Ombudsman said: "An
OL,17,Findependent investigation into the
OL,18,Fdeath of Benjamin Clarke at HMP Holme
OL,19,FHouse on 12 July 2025 has begun. We
OL,20,Fwill publish our final report after
OL,21,Fthe conclusion of Mr Clarke's inquest."
