OL,3,CMan jailed for threatening to kill MP
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FBenjamin Clarke was branded
OL,7,F"dangerous" in court earlier this year
OL,8,Fafter it was heard that he wanted to
OL,9,F"firebomb" the Bishop Auckland Labour
OL,10,FMP among other serious threats.
OL,12,FSam Rushworth reacted to Clarke's
OL,13,Fdeath saying: "At the moment all I can
OL,14,Freally say is that I am sad to hear
OL,15,Fthe news and my thoughts and
OL,16,Fcondolences are with Benjamin's family
OL,17,Fand friends.
OL,19,F"I have written to the Prisons
OL,20,FMinister to find out more details,
OL,21,Fbecause obviously it's concerning."
