OL,6,FClarke initially contacted Mr
OL,7,FRushworth last summer (2024) saying he
OL,8,Fwanted to lock him in a building and
OL,9,Fset fire to it.
OL,11,FIn March, Clarke admitted a second
OL,12,Fcharge whilst he was on bail of making
OL,13,Fthreats to kill against the Labour
OL,14,Fpolitician who was elected in the July
OL,15,F2024.
